== FactHarbor Application Demo  ==

(% class="box successmessage" %)
(((
**Live Demo of **
**[[app.FactHarbor.ch>>https://app.factharbor.ch]]**
)))

=== 1. User Experience: Submit & Explore ===

* **Submit a claim** — enter any text or URL, in any language
* **Job progress** — real-time stage-by-stage pipeline updates
* **Verdict overview** — overall assessment with truth percentage and confidence
* **Per-claim verdicts** — individual AtomicClaim results with evidence citations
* **Boundary findings** — how evidence clusters into ClaimAssessmentBoundaries
* **Evidence trail** — every source, every evidence item, fully traceable
* **Quality gates panel** — Gate 1 (claim validation) and Gate 4 (confidence tiering)

=== 2. Admin: Configuration & Control ===

* **Admin dashboard** — system overview and job management
* **Pipeline config** — tune analysis parameters at runtime (UCM)
* **Search config** — provider selection, query limits, fallback order
* **Calculation config** — weights, thresholds, aggregation rules
* **Config comparison** — diff between per-job snapshots and current defaults
* **Job history** — full audit trail with event log

=== 3. Source Reliability Database ===

* **SR overview** — cached domain evaluations across analyses
* **Domain lookup** — search any domain for its reliability assessment
* **Score breakdown** — multi-factor LLM evaluation per domain
* **Source types** — classification (peer-reviewed, news, official, etc.)
* **Impact on verdict** — how source reliability feeds into evidence weighting

