=== Source Reliability as Standalone Service ===

The SR module (domain credibility via multi-provider LLM) is designed for extraction as an independent API — serving other fact-checking platforms, newsrooms, researchers, and browser extensions.

=== Accessibility & Internationalization ===

|=Feature|=Target|=Why
|**WCAG 2.1 AA**|Beta+|Screen readers, keyboard nav, high-contrast
|**Multilingual UI (10+ languages)**|V1.0+|Match the multilingual analysis capability
|**RTL Language Support**|V1.5+|Arabic, Hebrew, and other RTL languages

